    "summary": "Conductor exposes a signed HTTP Data API at `https://api-universal.conductor.com/data-api/v1` plus an OAuth-protected remote MCP server at `https://mcp-universal.conductor.com/mcp/v2`; no public GraphQL API or CLI surfaced in its developer docs.",
