        "setup": "In Conductor, open Intelligence or Monitoring **Settings** and find **API keys and secrets**. The support article says API access must be enabled on your subscription; if you do not see API access, contact your Conductor account team or [Support](https://support.conductor.com/contact-us). Use the key as the `apiKey` query parameter.",
